   436→%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%
   437→%                                                                             %
   438→%                                                                             %
   439→%                                                                             %
   440→%   A c q u i r e M a g i c k M e m o r y                                     %
   441→%                                                                             %
   442→%                                                                             %
   443→%                                                                             %
   444→%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%
   445→%
   446→%  AcquireMagickMemory() returns a pointer to a block of memory at least size
   447→%  bytes suitably aligned for any use.
